\(x_{n}=\exp(-n/100)*n^{2}\cos(\pi n/3)\).

N<-1:1000
X<-ts(exp(-N/100)*N*N*cos(pi*1/3*N))
plot.ts(X)

.

Y<-2*X*X
Y.trend<-ma(Y, order = 6)
plot.ts(cbind(Y, Y.trend), plot.type = 'single', col = c('black', 'red'),lwd=c(1,2))
